rows.label: qst201709_0020
rows.name:
What the hell?
Don't tell me the training exercise is still going on.

rows.label: qst201709_0030
rows.name: I get it, I get it.

rows.label: qst201709_0040
rows.name:
I seem to remember we weren't the
only ones playing the bad guys, right?

rows.label: qst201709_0050
rows.name:
I'm sorry to ruin your fun everybody,
but we have already secured this area!

rows.label: qst201709_0070
rows.name:
Huh?! Just calm down a bit and look at us,
will you? Hello! We're on the same team!

rows.label: qst201709_0080
rows.name:
Um, Newt, it looks like these blighters
aren't playing around...

rows.label: qst201709_0100
rows.name:
These thugs must be hoping to take advantage of the
training exercise to try and assassinate the Emperor then?

rows.label: qst201709_0110
rows.name:
Doesn't look like they wanna talk,
but that's where my money is!

rows.label: qst201709_0120
rows.name: We can't let them lay a finger on His Majesty!

rows.label: qst201709_0140
rows.name: I may be only one Blade...

rows.label: qst201709_0150
rows.name:
But you'd have to cut off all four of my arms before
I let His Majesty the Emperor come to any harm!
